This demo shows some capabilities of the ECP Singularity container. 

wget http://tau.uoregon.edu/ecp.simg
module load singularity
singularity exec ./ecp.simg /bin/bash --rcfile /etc/bashrc

cd <demo> (This directory) 
cd NPB3.1; ./clean.sh; ./compile.sh; ./run.sh
cd ../mpi4py; ./run.sh
cd ../trilinos/MultiLevelPreconditioner_Maxwell; ./clean.sh; ./compile.sh ; ./run.sh


For further information, please contact:
Sameer Shende <sameer@cs.uoregon.edu>
